Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,到头来你还是要反抗我们么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:14.30,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(930,995)}thymia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就凭你这一个连情念力都使不了的小孩么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.25,0:03:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,旁边的也给我把武器扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,谁敢轻举妄动 我就切下这家伙的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,黎可斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,黎可斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,托库萨… 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,查克罗！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,快去把魂形干掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,欧尼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要拯救泥鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这是现在我最该考虑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,黎可斯 我们去！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,魂形就在 这里面…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有谁在？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,欧尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 尼比仔 蓬蓬头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.51,0:04:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼知道！ 而且不许叫我蓬蓬头！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这个时候突然袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 中计了么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不管那么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就由我们三个死守
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 尼比…仔？
